snippet.title: Best VGM 1566 - Shinobi III - Whirlwind
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Genesis
Shinobi III (1993)
Whirlwind
Hirofumi Murasaki, Masayuki Nagao & Morihiko Akiyama
